<#-- VeeMarker Macros Example -->

<#-- Define a simple greeting macro -->
<#macro greet name>
Hello, ${name}!
</#macro>

<#-- Define a user card macro with parameters -->
<#macro userCard user>
================================
Name: ${user.name}
Role: ${user.role}
Email: ${user.email}
================================
</#macro>

<#-- Define a product listing macro -->
<#macro productItem product>
Product: ${product.name}
Price: $${product.price}
Status: <#if product.in_stock>In Stock<#else>Out of Stock</#if>
</#macro>

<#-- Define a header macro that uses site data -->
<#macro pageHeader title>
========================================
${title}
========================================
Â© ${current_year} - ${site_title}
</#macro>

=====================================
Macros in VeeMarker
=====================================

1. Simple Macro Call
--------------------
<@greet name="World"/>
<@greet name="VeeMarker"/>

2. User Cards Using Macro
-------------------------
<#list users as user>
<@userCard user=user/>
</#list>

3. Product Listing
------------------
Available Products:

<#list products as product>
<@productItem product=product/>
---
</#list>

4. Page Header Macro
--------------------
<@pageHeader title="Welcome to Macros Example"/>

5. Nested Macro Usage
---------------------
<#macro teamSection team>
Team Members:
<#list team as member>
<@userCard user=member/>
</#list>
</#macro>

Our Team:
<@teamSection team=users/>

=====================================
End of Macros Example
=====================================